      Methods in mdxmlconverter.relationship that return TemporaryRelationship 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      static TemporaryRelationship AssociationConverter.convertAssociation(PackagedElement packagedElement, TemporaryModel tmpModel)
      Static method converting a given PackagedElement with the type 'uml:Association to an TemporaryRelationship
      If the given association is directed, a TemporaryRelationship with the two MemberEnds is created
      If the given association is directed, a TemporaryRelationship with the two MemberEnds and the OwnedEnd is created
      static TemporaryRelationship DependencyConverter.convertDependency(PackagedElement packagedElement, TemporaryModel tmpModel)
      Static method converting a given PackagedElement with type 'uml:Usage' to a TemporaryRelationship with references to the client and supplier and with type UmlRelationshipType.DEPENDENCY
      static TemporaryRelationship RelationshipConverter.convertRelationship(PackagedElement packagedElement, TemporaryModel tmpModel)
      Static method to convert PackagedElements of type 'uml:Association' and 'uml:Usage' to TemporaryRelationships Delegates the conversion of PackagedElements of type 'uml:Association' to the AssociationConverter Delegates the conversion of PackagedElements of type 'uml:Usage' to the DependencyConverter
